"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-01-team-gb-star-tears-interview-olympics-disqualification-21341043\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GB'sEmma Reid was in tears after a disqualification ended her hopes of winning anOlympicmedal in the women's judo.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.8374856634249082, \"rank\": 0.1940491435499208, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Semma\", \"score\": 0.9999998364508107, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"sEmma\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Semma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Semma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old, who won gold at theCommonwealth Gamestwo years ago, lost to South Korea's Hyunji Yoon\\u00a0in the opening round of the under-78kg event on Thursday morning.\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8630225758967353, \"rank\": 0.12756068824316225, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reid receiving two penalties inside the opening two minutes of the contest for non-combativity and a false attack before receiving her third during the golden score period - resulting in her disqualification.\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Reid's exit has now ended Team GB's chances of winning a judo medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.8374856634249082, \"rank\": 0.1940491435499208, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 645, \"end\": 650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999986785042, \"rank\": 1.321581537383134e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think we had a really good preparation.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were at home, we went away for a camp.\", \"from\": 696, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think it's tough, especially when a few of us, it's our first Games.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are not seeded so you can get anyone first fight.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have beaten her (Yoon) before so it's frustrating that I could have got to the next round but I think we all felt good going into it.\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just sometimes it does not happen on the day.'\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked what she will do next, Reid replied: 'I think I will just reflect on the competition, I am just upset I could not make a better day of it.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'But rest and decompress from everything.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a tough three years, four years, well, my life really.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am just proud of myself for getting to this point\\u2026 sorry.'\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Reid then covered her face as she began to cry before adding: 'Yeah, I think I am just going to rest up and go again.'\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC reporter attempted to console her by saying: 'You are an Olympian, no one can take that away from you.'\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9871280545757096, \"rank\": 0.011688619551047344, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1560, \"end\": 1568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999930507345189, \"rank\": 6.948658722777765e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Why is Matt Baker commentating on Olympic gymnastics?\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1747, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Baker_(artist)\", \"score\": 0.9803545262362454, \"rank\": 0.01665365599791718, \"text\": \"Matt Baker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http: